g in the same way on\nall strategies), the differences in the mortalities in the focal interaction\nwill lead to different distributions of roles for different strategies. This\nleads to more complex rules for cooperation than the classical Hamilton's rule.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 1 Dec 2019 23:18:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-03"}
