lues between 95% and 99% for the different attack scenarios.\nFinally, the performance analysis demonstrates that the use of the proposed\nframework has minimal overhead on the smart grid devices' computing resources.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Dec 2019 01:00:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-03"}
