ing. Namely, for a suitable class of\nsolutions in one space-dimension, we prove the lower estimate\n$\\|u_x(t)\\|_\\infty \\geq C(T-t)^{-2/(p-2)}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Dec 2019 08:29:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-03"}
