 under tensile loading also\nexhibit cross-slip activity in twinned nanopillars. However, this cross-slip\nactivity occurs only through Fleischer mechanism and no Friedel-Escaig\nmechanism of cross-slip has been observed under tensile loading.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Dec 2019 11:26:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-03"}
