 63% of V100's peak\nperformance and 24% of Titan Z's peak performance for stencil kernels over\ngrids with 256 points. Our study reveals that improving memory usage should be\nthe most efficient strategy for leveraging the performance of the implemented\nsolution on the evaluated architectures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Dec 2019 11:45:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-05"}
