 flow modes can provide additional\ndiscriminatory power in the study of initial conditions as well as new\nstringent constraints to hydrodynamical calculations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Dec 2019 13:04:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Jul 2020 13:58:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-02"}
