s of B-mode images offered\nby our method compared to those by a commercial scanner, and hence, it may\nsignificantly improve the diagnostic quality of ultrasound images.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Dec 2019 14:21:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 19 Feb 2020 13:47:01 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 30 May 2020 14:32:09 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 29 Sep 2021 16:00:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-30"}
